channel.title: How do I remove my server from the server status list?
channel.description: Thats my only question. I will explain though. My bro has his server on one computer and I have my server on the one I'm posting this on. Next is the fact that he started his server first and is on like page 24 of the server status list. Now even when I'm trying to advertise on a different computer and a different ip adress (Though the adresses are only a few numbers different) it will still say you only get one post one server. Any help? :confused: :confused:
